item.title: cvxpy
item.description: Summary I contributed an interface for CoinOR’s Cbc MIP-solver (based on cylp) including examples, tests and continuous-integration scripts. This was merged into master and the upcoming 1.0 will have some changes (already merged). Additionally, there is an unmerged pull-request to integrate an MIQP-solver based on CoinOR’s Bonmin and my project pyMIQP.
